				<p>Erin, if you wanted a similar effect to the tomato paste, you could try using a sweet pepper paste instead. The Balkan version is called Ajvar and is usually made with either just the sweet peppers, or sometimes with eggplant and sweet peppers. I&#8217;ve used both versions to cook with for taste and thickening purposes. I note Amazon sells Ajvar, if you can&#8217;t find it anywhere else.</p>
